scenes.description: Mori Calliope, Takanashi Kiara, and Ninomae Ina'nis discuss their performances and announce the upcoming music video premiere for the 5th-anniversary song 'Fortune Spinner'.
The group begins celebrating their 5th anniversary. A large cake and trophies appear on stage, and they decide to hold a self-styled award ceremony to commemorate their time together.
Takanashi Kiara presents her 'Most Meals Cooked Award' and gives a short speech about her lifestyle and her gratitude toward her Gen-mates.
Ninomae Ina'nis presents her 'Most Time Spent on the Floor Award' and thanks the audience and her Gen-mates for their support over the years.
Mori Calliope presents her 'Best Worst Luck Award' and shares her determination regarding her luck in games with microtransactions.
